   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mobile classroom empowers 1000+ kids in Langa CT</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide online literacy programmes for primary school learners from the impoverished, Langa community.  South Africa has an unequal education system and high drop-out rate which perpetuates the cycle of poverty. This mobile classroom, equipped with 40 laptops &amp; 2 teaching stations  will support 5 Langa schools in the Langa Township, offering programmes that will utilise the expertise &amp; materials of leading school, Bishops Diocesan College.</narrative>
  </description>
